  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You throw your hands forward creating a compressed blast of air assisting you in a variety of physical tasks; from escaping, fending off an attack, or dispersing a hazardous gas.</p><p>As a reaction, when you are forced to make a Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution saving throw or skill check against a Ninjutsu or Taijutsu, you instead use your Ninjutsu ability modifier in place of your Strength, Dexterity or Constitution for the triggering roll.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3. If cast at C-Rank you add your proficiency to the roll if you aren't already proficient. If cast at B-Rank you may select another creature within 20 feet of you to gain the benefits of this jutsu, using your Ability modifier and proficiency bonus. If cast at A-Rank, creatures benefiting from this jutsu roll at advantage. If cast at S-Rank, all creatures of your choice within 30 feet of you can gain this jutsu's benefit.</p>",
